*Istragu* je sprovela istražna komisija. (The investigation was conducted by the investigative commission.)

Policija je počela *istragu* u vezi sa slučajem. (The police started the investigation in connection with the case.)

Ona je nastavila *istragu* na terenu. (She continued the investigation on the ground.)

Oni su završili *istragu* u roku. (They finished the investigation on time.)

Ova *istraga* će trajati nekoliko meseci. (This investigation will last for several months.)